CODE:
import java.util.*;
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args){
        Scanner obj=new Scanner(System.in);
        System.out.println("whether the input is onside or outside of 10");
        while(true){
            int n=obj.nextInt();
            if(n<1||n>10)
                continue;
            System.out.println(n + "is between 0 and 10");
            break;
        }

    }
}
OUTPUT:
whether the input is onside or outside of 10
22
3
3is between 0 and 10
